A Python CLI/library generated from the Artemis `py-tool` template. Managed with
[uv](https://docs.astral.sh/uv/).

## Develop

```bash
uv sync              # create .venv and install dev dependencies from the lockfile
uv run {{ project_name }}   # run the console script
```

## Gates (run before pushing; CI runs them too)

```bash
uv run ruff check .        # lint
uv run ruff format --check .  # format
uv run pyright             # typecheck (strict)
uv run pytest --cov        # test with coverage
```

CI runs the shared Artemis pipelines (`ci`, `security`{% if visibility == 'public' %}, `codeql`{% endif %}) on every PR via
[ci-python.yml](https://github.com/willzhu16/platform). Behaviour is customised through
tool config in `pyproject.toml` (ruff, pyright, pytest), never by renaming commands.
